      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The side-effect of which of the following drug is used as a therapeutic advantage in alopecia?</span></span></p>",
